{
  "texts": [
    "Four different scenes were selected, namely a Grass, an airplane, and a storage tank.",
    "As shown in the first row of figures, the RCA network with channel attention achieves more precise localization of important areas for airplane, grass, and storage tank categories while minimizing interference from low-priority features.",
    "Furthermore, despite the challenging task of distinguishing between the grass and non-grass regions, the proposed network including channel attention demonstrates improved control over crucial areas for these categories.",
    "These results indicate the effectiveness of the channel attention mechanism and the robust image feature representation capabilities of the RCA Network.",
    "DiscussionIn this section, we delve into the outcomes derived from the experimental results presented in Tables 123."
  ]
}